<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Thank You — Whips Washing</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Rajdhani:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --black: #080808;
      --gold: #c9a84c;
      --gold-light: #e8c97a;
      --white: #f0ece4;
      --muted: #7a7570;
      --border: #1e1e1e;
      --font-display: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
      --font-serif: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      --font-body: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
    }
    body {
      background: var(--black);
      color: var(--white);
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    .logo img { height: 80px; filter: invert(1); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
    .icon { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    h1 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      color: var(--white);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .gold-line {
      width: 60px;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--gold);
      margin: 1.2rem auto;
    }
    p {
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 480px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }
    .contact-note {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    .btn {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--black);
      background: var(--gold);
      padding: 1rem 2.4rem;
      border-radius: 1px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }
    .btn:hover { background: var(--gold-light); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="logo"><img src="Whips_Washing.png" alt="Whips Washing" /></div>
  <div class="icon">✦</div>
  <h1>THANK YOU</h1>
  <div class="gold-line"></div>
  <p>Your quote request has been received. We'll review your details and get back to you shortly.</p>
  <p class="contact-note">In the meantime, feel free to reach us directly at <strong style="color:var(--white);">(316) 249-0040</strong> or <strong style="color:var(--white);">whipswashing@gmail.com</strong></p>
  <a href="index.html" class="btn">Back to Home</a>
</body>
</html>
